From Danny Keren Subject Re Desertification of the Negev This is I lived in the Negev for many years and I can say for sure that no Beduins were moved or harmed in any On the contrary their standard of living has climbed sharply many of them now live in rather nice permanent houses and own There are quite a few Beduin students in the Ben Gurion There are good friendly relations between them and the rest of the All the Beduins I met would be rather surprised to read Davidson's poster I have to Danny